#: org.kde.arianna.appdata.xml:14
msgid ""
"An ebook reader and library management app supporting \".epub\" files. "
"Arianna discovers your books automatically, and sorts them by categories, "
"genres and authors."
msgstr ""
"Un lector de ebook de app gerente de bibliotheca supportante files de \".epub"
"\". Arianna discopere tu libros automaticamente, e los ordina per "
"categorias, generes e autores."

